{"tid":676091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：阿叔搶手袋被擒 「我跑步咋」博鬆人","createTime":"2018-05-24T06:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:33:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3baf09144c59e90293feeb888d8693edd516ba76","tid":676091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399989&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7c120fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399989&h=9965c976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399989</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月24日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：阿叔搶手袋被擒<br />\n「我跑步咋」博鬆人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=ca4e3842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■偷袋賊被三名熱心市民按柱生擒。讀者阿Cat提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小記真係好憎男人蝦女人，特別係嗰啲有手有腳，仲要搶女人嘢嘅社會寄生蟲，唔好意思，小記太有正義感，激動咗少少㖭！其實唔怪我小記勞氣，喺前日就有個男人，光天化日下，當街當巷搶一個阿姐嘅手袋，好彩俾幾位真漢子捉住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起飛腳逃走不果<br />\n<br />\n住喺荃灣福來邨永昌樓嘅讀者阿Cat，喺前日下晝4點幾，行樓梯去到3樓，突然聽到有人大喝：「阿婆嘅嘢你都搶？」阿Cat望出去對面嘅永康樓，發現有幾個男人企咗喺度，其中一個着牛仔褲嘅阿叔俾兩個人㩒埋燈柱，着住白色制服嘅哥仔似係附近餐廳嘅職員，<br />\n<br />\n疑似偷袋賊郁身郁勢，仲起飛腳踢向左邊嘅黑衫熱心男，擺明想鬆人，邊有咁易吖！三位哥仔眼明手快，好快又將阿叔捉住，見拳腳唔等使，阿叔竟然用演技，坐咗喺花槽欄杆，<br />\n仲話「我跑步咋嘛」，做戲做全套，仲喺後褲袋拎咗支水出嚟飲，之但係，就算有演技都要配合造型㗎，着牛仔褲跑步係咩style呢？<br />\n<br />\n小記八到啲料，原來有位女士喺福來邨俾牛仔褲阿叔搶手袋，雙方一路拉扯去到永康樓，有幾位猛男見義勇為捉住阿叔，Cat話熱心男動作敏捷，有街坊估佢可能係便衣探員，<br />\n而被人搶嘢嘅女士，其實仲好後生嘅，同賊仔拉扯時應該整親隻手，見佢同在場阿Sir邊講邊搓手踭，真係陰功豬！Cat住咗喺福來邨近30年，都係第一次見到有人光天化日搶嘢咁猖狂。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人話，被捕男子姓蔡（55歲），涉嫌企圖搶劫姓王女子（46歲），案件已經交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：金紫荊又開片　影相檔四男混戰"},{"pid":"5e6e4aa4d3e59b8e7a6fc7ac62bff4b09c2daf15","tid":676091,"uid":129506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"阿婆嘅嘢你都搶？」<br />\n<br />\n46歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168a40e46a4f2a889b5069b32783f7628639cf72","tid":676091,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6e4aa4d3e59b8e7a6fc7ac62bff4b09c2daf15","tid":676091,"uid":129506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"阿婆嘅嘢你都搶？」<br />\n<br />\n46歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"嬲嬲豬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ba264e3dad2d0a8f1b015357109d2c48cb1987","tid":676091,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"168a40e46a4f2a889b5069b32783f7628639cf72","tid":676091,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6e4aa4d3e59b8e7a6fc7ac62bff4b09c2daf15","tid":676091,"uid":129506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"阿婆嘅嘢你都搶？」<br />\n<br />\n46歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"嬲嬲豬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"姓王女子即刻唔想認俾人搶手袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64047d0ce5bc90a37c1a628f38eadbd2983b90ff","tid":676091,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ba264e3dad2d0a8f1b015357109d2c48cb1987","tid":676091,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1